verbose_text: Therefore, free GST protein was used as a negative control in a qualitative pull-down assay to test the functionality of the GST-SPX1 and verify the previously observed Pi dependent interaction between recombinant AtSPX1 and MBP-AtdPHR1 [XREF_BIBR] Quantification showed that 1.5- and 3.5-fold more GST-SPX1 is present in elution fractions E1 and E2 in the presence of phosphate compared with the absence of phosphate.
evidence: interaction between recombinant AtSPX1 and MBP-AtdPHR1
